---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Gabriele Pellegrini
---

<div class="container">
  <section class="intro">
    <h1>{{ title }}</h1>
    <p>Breve descrizione su di te e il tuo lavoro. Una presentazione professionale che descriva chi sei e cosa fai.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="tags-section">
    <h2>Tags</h2>
    <div class="tags-list">
      {% for tag, posts in collections | dichotomize %}
        {% if tag != "all" and tag != "posts" %}
          <a href="/tags/{{ tag }}/" class="tag">
            {{ tag }} <sup>{{ posts.length }}</sup>
          </a>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="posts-section">
    <h2>Recent Posts</h2>
    <div class="posts-list">
      {% set recentPosts = collections.posts | slice(0, 5) %}
      {% for post in recentPosts %}
        <article class="post-item">
          <div class="post-meta">
            <time datetime="{{ post.date | formatDate }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
          </div>
          <h3 class="post-title">
            <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
          </h3>
          {% if post.data.description %}
            <p class="post-excerpt">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
          {% endif %}
        </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    <p class="more-link"><a href="/journal/">View all posts â†’</a></p>
  </section>
</div>